    <p><span class="bold">Bill Number:</span> C-321</p>
    <p><span class="bold">Current Status:</span> House of Commons bill awaiting first reading in the Senate</p>
    <p><span class="bold">Last Major Stage Completed:</span> Third reading in the House of Commons</p>
    <p><span class="bold">Parliament Session:</span> 44th Parliament, 1st session</p>

