    <h2>Bill Number: C-258</h2>

    <h3>Status</h3>
    <p class="status">Current Status: Outside the Order of Precedence</p>
    <p>Last Major Stage Completed: First reading in the House of Commons</p>

    <h3>Parliament Session</h3>
