    <h3>Readings</h3>
    <p><strong>Senate Readings:</strong> First - Not Completed, Second - Not Completed, Third - Not Completed</p>
    <p><strong>House Readings:</strong> First - Completed, Second - Not Completed, Third - Not Completed</p>
