<h1>An Act respecting the development of a national strategy to assess, prevent and address environmental racism and to advance environmental justice</h1>

<h2>Bill Information</h2>
<p><strong>Bill Number:</strong> C-226</p>
<p><strong>Current Status:</strong> National Strategy Respecting Environmental Racism and Environmental Justice Act</p>
<p><strong>Last Major Stage Completed:</strong> At consideration in committee in the Senate</p>
